high_descs: Go to the coffee maker in front of you.
Take the coffee cup from the coffee maker.
Go to the sink to the left of the coffee maker.
Fill the cup with water in the sink.
Place the coffee cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup of water in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Pick up the mug from the coffee machine
Bring the mug to the sink.
Fill up the mug with water in the sink.
Bring the mug to the coffee machine
Set the mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Fill the mug with water for the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn right and move towards the door and turn left and move past the counter and turn left and move toward the oven and then turn right and move towards and face the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug from the coffee maker.
Turn left move towards the microwave then turn right and move towards and face the sink.
Place the mug in the sink, turn on the water, turn off the water, and then pick up the mug from the sink.
Turn right and move forward past the sink and then turn left and face the coffee maker.
Place the mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug of water in the coffee maker.
